author: Pam London
title: Saturday’s prep soccer results
text:
Curtis 5, Rogers 0 
Morgan Weaver scored three goals to lead Curtis over Rogers in an SPSL 4A game. Maddie Lockwood and Brooke Weber also scored for the Vikings.
Puyallup 2, Emerald Ridge 0 
Katelynn Wood had a goal and an assist for Puyallup in an SPSL 4A win over Emerald Ridge. Sunny Bieber recorded the second goal for the Vikings.
For complete results, visit http://seattletimes.sportngin.com/schedule/day/league_instance/32091?subseason=226761 .
